Emacsed is an ed(1)-like editing mode for Emacsen. It might also be the only ed implementation with syntax highlighting. It's available at http://aon.iki.fi/files/emacsed/emacsed.el
(which appears to be down, but still available from http://web.archive.org/web/20070221113930/http://aon.iki.fi/files/emacsed/emacsed.el ).

